text:
First time experience: The place is not so easy to find for the first time, once got it is easy. From Serangoon MRT just a 317 bus to reach the place, is convenience.

The most that make me to recommend is the in charge is friendly and helpful. The place is good, clean and quiet.
Norah is passionate about teaching the kids and is generous with her time and energy. My two kids 2 years and 4 years old love her dance classes!
Great place and Teachers!! I am always looking forward to my class and enjoy it so much ğŸ¥°
My kids enjoy the dance lessons.  They had zero knowledge when they first started. Now they can dance to the beat or any beats!
